3. Privy prompts user to sign via Phantom
4. Transaction submitted to Solana network
5. Lighthouse program executes, triggers event
6. Backend API receives event notification
7. Backend queries memo field: "ref:c5772352"
8. Backend credits user's internal balance
9. WebSocket notifies frontend: "Balance updated"
10. User can now place bets with credited funds

